Timing and Scheduling

Schedule the village session the day AFTER the main talk.

Reasoning:

People inspired by the main talk have time to find you
Word of mouth spreads overnight
The AMSAT Village crowd will already know about it

Ideal slot: afternoon or early evening.

Evening works well because:

People are more relaxed
Willing to stay for discussion
The hack session can run into the night naturally

